1. *Verovali* smo da će nas vreme poslužiti za izlet. (We believed that the weather would be good for our trip.)
2. Ja ne bih *verovala* da možeš da završiš ovaj posao sam. (I wouldn't have believed that you could finish this task on your own.)
3. Da li ti *veruješ* u natprirodne pojave? (Do you believe in supernatural phenomena?)
4. Oni *su verovali* da će dobiti priliku da igraju na najvećoj pozornici. (They believed that they would get a chance to perform on the biggest stage.)
5. *Verujem* da ćeš uspeti u svojim planovima. (I believe that you will succeed in your plans.)
6. Mi smo *verovali* u pobedu naše fudbalske reprezentacije. (We believed in the victory of our football team.)
7. Kada su *verovali* da je sve gotovo, dogodio se preokret. (When they believed that everything was over, a turnaround happened.)
8. Nije teško *verovati* u ljubav kada si zaljubljen. (It's not hard to believe in love when you're in love.)
9. *Verujete li* da postoji život posle smrti? (Do you believe that there is life after death?)
10. Oni *nisu verovali* da će dobiti posao, ali su ipak pokušali. (They didn't believe that they would get the job, but they still tried.)